sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Supervisore
    participant API as Server REST /api
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant WS as WS broadcast

    Admin->>API: POST /api/scores/increment<br/>{ playerName, roundId }
    API->>DB: Score.findOneAndUpdate({tournamentName, playerName})
    API->>DB: Round.updateOne($addToSet: winnerNames)
    API->>WS: broadcast score_update(tournamentName, playerName, score)
    WS-->>Admin: WS score_update(...)
    WS-->>Players: WS score_update(...)

